
## VOLARE PIPELINE

An R template for running pairwise cross-domain regression screens and assembling the output into JSON files compatible with VOLARE. \n
Define your predictor domains, outcomes, and covariates.

The script handles the regression loop, significance filtering, mPlot line endpoint computation, influence diagnostics, and JSON packaging. \n
Designed for multi-omic datasets to visually explore which baseline variables predict longitudinal outcomes.
